reviewText: Same as before... wouldn't waste my $ on this.

Bob West is the man. This DVD is just what needed as I am currently trying to whoa train and force fetch our 6 month old GSP. I would highly recommend this video to anyone who is trying to train their own bird dog.

It's a great dvd for information on training dogs.  I found it very useful!  I bought with the dvd about puppy training.  both were very well done.  If you love training hunting dogs, this is for you.
I've watched this video a few times already.  Now it's time to execute a plan that will copy the examples he shows.  It's very up-to-date.
